        <item>
            <title>【實試】Dyson OnTrac 降噪耳機　主動降噪消除 40dB + 佩戴非常舒適</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/07/18/dyson-ontrac/mobile-music/headphones/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=dyson-ontrac</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/07/18/dyson-ontrac/mobile-music/headphones/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Oscar]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Thu, 18 Jul 2024 06:01:06 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[流動音樂]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[音樂耳機]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Dyson]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Dyson OnTrac]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[無線藍牙耳機]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1250555</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>Dyson 今日宣佈推出首款高保真、純音頻的降噪耳機 Dyson OnTrac。這款耳機具有先進的降噪功能，更備有長達 55 小時特強續航力，充電一次可使用 2 星期。今日 Dyson 就邀請了小嫻和小編親身體驗 Dyson OnTrac。</p><p><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1250839" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/1-26-580x580.jpg" alt="" width="580" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/1-26-580x580.jpg 580w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/1-26.jpg 900w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/1-26-144x144.jpg 144w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 580px" /></p><h2>寬廣音頻範圍</h2><p>Dyson OnTrac 配備 40 mm、16 ohm 的釹合金喇叭驅動器，可重現低至 6Hz 和高達 21,000 Hz 的頻率，呈現深沉低音和清晰高音的細膩音色。</p><p><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1250895" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/11-580x580.jpg" alt="" width="580" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/11-580x580.jpg 580w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/11.jpg 900w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/11-144x144.jpg 144w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 580px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲釹合金喇叭驅動器</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1250896" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/4-9-580x580.jpg" alt="" width="580" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/4-9-580x580.jpg 580w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/4-9.jpg 900w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/4-9-144x144.jpg 144w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 580px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲揚聲器外殼配合耳朵傾斜 13 度，營造更直接的音效體驗。</p><h2>8 個主動降噪麥克風　可消除 40 dB 噪音</h2><p>Dyson OnTrac 採用個人化主動降噪演算法，使用 8 個主動降噪麥克風，每秒對外部聲音進行達 384,000 次取樣。配合優質材料和精心設計的內部幾何結構，耳機可消除 40 dB 噪音。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1250894" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/10-580x580.jpg" alt="" width="580" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/10-580x580.jpg 580w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/10.jpg 900w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/10-144x144.jpg 144w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 580px" /></p><br /><b>相關文章:</b><blockquote><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/04/18/dyson-supersonic-nural/pretty01/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">Dyson Supersonic Nural 新一代智能風筒香港發佈  3 大智能感測科技、按距離調温保護頭皮</a></li>&nbsp;</blockquote><br /><h2>可個人化變換耳機外殼及耳墊</h2><p>Dyson OnTrac 有四種配色，現提供亮銀色、亮銅色和黑鋼色等配色選項。陶瓷硃砂色則採用了陶瓷質感的噴漆表面處理。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1250821" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/dysonontracheadphone-2-630x580.jpg" alt="" width="630" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/dysonontracheadphone-2-630x580.jpg 630w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/dysonontracheadphone-2-scaled.jpg 978w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 630px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲多種顏色和飾面</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1250834" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/dysonontracheadphone-10-694x389.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="389" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/dysonontracheadphone-10-694x389.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/dysonontracheadphone-10.jpeg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1250901" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/12-6-473x580.jpg" alt="" width="473" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/12-6-473x580.jpg 473w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/12-6.jpg 734w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 473px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1250879" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/14-580x580.jpg" alt="" width="580" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/14-580x580.jpg 580w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/14.jpg 900w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/14-144x144.jpg 144w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 580px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1250880" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/15-580x580.jpg" alt="" width="580" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/15-580x580.jpg 580w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/15.jpg 900w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/15-144x144.jpg 144w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 580px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1250881" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/16-580x580.jpg" alt="" width="580" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/16-580x580.jpg 580w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/16.jpg 900w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/16-144x144.jpg 144w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 580px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1250882" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/17-580x580.jpg" alt="" width="580" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/17-580x580.jpg 580w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/17.jpg 900w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/17-144x144.jpg 144w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 580px" /></p><h2></h2><h2>佩戴感：不覺夾耳　三點式分佈平衡重量</h2><p>小編初初看見 Dyson OnTrac 時覺得耳機看起來很大，以為肯定會很笨重，但實際佩戴時居然意想不到的輕盈。試戴最先感受到的是其平衡的重量分佈設計。一般頭戴式耳機重量不是集中在頭頂，就是會過份「夾耳」，但 Dyson OnTrac 採用三點式分佈設計，重量平均分佈在雙耳和頭頂，佩戴時不會覺得有任何位置特別受力。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1250878" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/3-11-580x580.jpg" alt="" width="580" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/3-11-580x580.jpg 580w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/3-11.jpg 900w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/3-11-144x144.jpg 144w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 580px" /></p><p>耳墊的材質讓小編印象深刻。耳墊海綿非常軟熟，官方稱其為「微絨面」，實際觸感類似滑身麖皮，非常親膚，材質摸起來似乎應該不會起毛粒。耳墊採用「高密度泡棉」，柔軟之餘回彈力強，大力按壓後亦可迅速回復原狀（見下面影片），提供極舒適的佩戴感，長時間佩戴應該不會覺得耳朵疼痛。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1250871" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/18-580x580.jpg" alt="" width="580" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/18-580x580.jpg 580w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/18.jpg 900w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/18-144x144.jpg 144w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 580px" /></p><div style="padding: 100% 0 0 0; position: relative;"><iframe style="position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; width: 100%; height: 100%;" title="dyson_OnTrac_耳墊" src="https://player.vimeo.com/video/985431167?badge=0&amp;autopause=0&amp;player_id=0&amp;app_id=58479" frameborder="0"></iframe></div><p><script src="https://player.vimeo.com/api/player.js"></script></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲「高密度泡棉」耳墊</p><p>剛剛戴上頭時會感覺到頭帶有些微壓力，但在調校好頭帶長度後，配合特厚海綿「卸力」，小編沒有特別覺得不舒服。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1250897" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/6-6-580x580.jpg" alt="" width="580" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/6-6-580x580.jpg 580w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/6-6.jpg 900w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/6-6-144x144.jpg 144w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 580px" /></p><div style="text-align: center;">▲可調式頭帶 + 特厚海綿</div><div></div><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1250873" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/13-580x580.jpg" alt="" width="580" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/13-580x580.jpg 580w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/13.jpg 900w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/13-144x144.jpg 144w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 580px" /></p><div style="text-align: center;">▲頭帶採用多軸萬向式支架設計確保重量平均分佈</div><div></div><div style="padding: 100% 0 0 0; position: relative;"><iframe style="position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; width: 100%; height: 100%;" title="dyson_OnTrac_test 頭帶" src="https://player.vimeo.com/video/985431117?badge=0&amp;autopause=0&amp;player_id=0&amp;app_id=58479" frameborder="0"></iframe></div><p><script src="https://player.vimeo.com/api/player.js"></script></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲頭帶的海綿非常軟熟</p><p>音色方面，小編今次僅是走馬看花，蜻蜓點水式試聽過一陣，無法給予太多意見，但粗略來説 Dyson OnTrac 人聲表現清晰，音色細膩，高頻部分尤為突出。</p><h2>其他功能</h2><ul><li>頭部感應：當用家取下耳機時，電容式感測器會自動偵測，並發出暫停音訊的信號。重新戴上耳機後，則自動恢復音訊。</li><li>直觀的操控桿：可輕鬆播放、暫停、跳過、快進和倒退曲目，或按住進行語音指令。</li><li>清晰的通話：雙波束形成的麥克風能清晰地接收你的聲音，而非外界噪音。</li><li>實時聲音追蹤：持續監測耳內和外界音量，並通過應用程式中的即時報告顯示可能有害的高音量。</li></ul><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1250966 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/2-17-580x580.jpg" alt="" width="580" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/2-17-580x580.jpg 580w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/2-17.jpg 900w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/2-17-144x144.jpg 144w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 580px" /></p><br /><b>相關文章:</b><blockquote><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/04/18/dyson-supersonic-nural/pretty01/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">Dyson Supersonic Nural 新一代智能風筒香港發佈  3 大智能感測科技、按距離調温保護頭皮</a></li>&nbsp;</blockquote><br /><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/07/18/dyson-ontrac/mobile-music/headphones/">【實試】Dyson OnTrac 降噪耳機　主動降噪消除 40dB + 佩戴非常舒適</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
            </description>
