            <title>網絡攝錄機有效助亂拋垃圾執法　食環署擬再加裝 17 部攝錄機</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/07/17/cameras-helped-with-littering-enforcement/life-tech/smartcity/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=cameras-helped-with-littering-enforcement</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/07/17/cameras-helped-with-littering-enforcement/life-tech/smartcity/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Ngan Ivan]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Wed, 17 Jul 2024 14:00:46 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[智慧城市]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[環保]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[亂拋垃圾]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[網絡攝錄機]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[食環署]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1250923</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p style="font-weight: 400;">早前食環署向東區區議會提交的文件中提到，目前在全港 450 個非法棄置垃圾黑點設置網絡攝錄機，可記錄違法時間和相關車輛資料，能有效分析違規者的模式並協助執法。相關措施實施後頗見成效，計劃於北角加裝攝錄機。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1250937 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/1-29-694x411.jpg" alt="亂拋垃圾" width="694" height="411" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/1-29-694x411.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/1-29.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1250939 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/2-16-694x441.jpg" alt="亂拋垃圾" width="694" height="441" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/2-16-694x441.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/2-16.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">圖片來源：<a href="https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1678846-20221207.htm">RTHK</a></p><p style="font-weight: 400;">食環署計劃於北角的 4 個黑點加裝攝錄機，分別是過去一年接獲了 22 宗亂拋垃圾投訴僅能撿控 11 宗的英皇道近糖水道、43 宗投訴檢控 26 宗的糖水道近春秧街、3 宗投訴無檢控的英皇道近東匯坊以及 13 宗投訴但檢控高達 69 宗的錦屏街。筲箕灣南安街公廁對出違法情況嚴重，在加裝攝錄機後過去 1 年錄得 177 宗檢控，北角道與春秧街和渣華道交界亦錄得 70 宗。</p><p style="font-weight: 400;">食環署亦計劃將北角英皇道近健康東街列作後備的加裝攝錄機地點，當有地點的亂拋垃圾情況得到改善，攝錄機的錄影服務將會移到其他地點，原有的機器將保留以便日後有恢復服務的需要。</p><p style="font-weight: 400;">資料來源：<a href="https://std.stheadline.com/realtime/article/2011460/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82-%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E-%E7%B6%B2%E7%B5%A1%E6%94%9D%E9%8C%84%E6%A9%9F%E6%8D%89%E5%9E%83%E5%9C%BE%E8%9F%B2%E6%95%88%E6%9E%9C%E9%A1%AF%E8%91%97-%E9%A3%9F%E7%92%B0%E7%BD%B2%E5%BB%BA%E8%AD%B0%E5%8C%97%E8%A7%924%E5%80%8B%E9%BB%91%E9%BB%9E%E5%86%8D%E5%8A%A0%E8%A3%9D?fbclid=IwZXh0bgNhZW0CMTAAAR2wn-YCwZE-Mw8d9q-SK8mw0w4O82IFUk3sl-xVNJbFfGO2a7g4hqNRNlk_aem_2z1faKToHF8R8_8VaS_y7g">星島</a></p><p>圖片來源：<a href="https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1724223-20231022.htm">RTHK</a></p><br /><b>相關文章:</b><blockquote><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/06/27/security-bureau-plan-to-set-up-2000-cctv-in-hk-each-year/tech-secure/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">保安局擬每年全港安裝 2000 部 CCTV　鄧炳強：情況允許或會再增設數目</a></li>&nbsp;</blockquote><br /><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/07/17/cameras-helped-with-littering-enforcement/life-tech/smartcity/">網絡攝錄機有效助亂拋垃圾執法　食環署擬再加裝 17 部攝錄機</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
